						               													<description>&amp;quot;Even though you don't see us, we are four factions soaring through the atmosphere searching for perfect thunders to record. In this game you're one of us! Your goal is to create thunder and record that beautiful sound of ephemeral energy flowing to planet earth&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Thunder Visitors is a game that can be printed on a single sheet (both a low and a full ink version are available). It can be played solo or with two or three players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Your goal is to manage the cards in your hand and manipulate your die on the grid so you can create thunder and score points while recording it.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players select cards and compare cards simultaneously to determine which actions they can play. By combining 4 different elements depicted on their cards, they create thunder which they can record.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Thunder Visitors combines a puzzle (pattern building) with simultaneous action selection (bidding for actions and playing order), that also works well when played solo.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
